# Auto-generate DOCX report

This repo contains a Python script and a GitHub Actions workflow that will build a Word document (DOCX) directly in the repository.

How to use
1. Go to the Actions tab.
2. Run the workflow named `Build DOCX` (“Run workflow”).
3. Wait 1-2 minutes. The file will be committed to `docs/《Python程序设计》课程实践作业.docx`.

Local build (optional)
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python report_generator.py --out "docs/《Python程序设计》课程实践作业.docx" \
  --term "2025 - 2026学年第1学期" \
  --klass "2023级物联网工程1班" \
  --sid "230911005" \
  --name "张三" \
  --teacher "李晓"
```
